The featured recipe in this project is a delicious Italian pasta served with rich tomato sauce and a generous topping of cheese. The image of pasta on the homepage gives visitors a warm and appetizing welcome, encouraging them to explore more recipes. By using free and valid image links from platforms like Unsplash, Pixabay, and Pexels, the website feels visually appealing and realistic. This enhances the user experience, making the recipe book not only informative but also engaging and professional in presentation.
